projection.

00:04:37.410 --> 00:04:39.510
So if we had this, for
example, in Singapore,

00:04:39.510 --> 00:04:41.130
then I would, in
principle, appear

00:04:41.130 --> 00:04:42.660
as if I'm standing over there.

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:45.770
This, of course, is still at
the science fiction stage,

00:04:45.770 --> 00:04:48.340
but a lot of people
are working on it.

00:04:48.340 --> 00:04:51.990
