00:50:37.330 --> 00:50:39.060
Actually, it's very interesting.

00:50:39.060 --> 00:50:41.450
I did my graduate in Greece.

00:50:41.450 --> 00:50:43.500
And over there, the
professors were very careful.

00:50:43.500 --> 00:50:47.160
So here, they would have
written 39.6, or whatever

00:50:47.160 --> 00:50:48.928
it is-- the actual number.

00:50:48.928 --> 00:50:50.720
Then, I went to graduate
school at Caltech.

00:50:50.720 --> 00:50:54.970
And I took my first class
in quantum electronics

00:50:54.970 --> 00:50:57.020
by a fellow called
Amnom Yariv, who

00:50:57.020 --> 00:50:59.300
