00:52:12.110 --> 00:52:16.850
So you see now why light
frequency is very important

00:52:16.850 --> 00:52:19.210
when it comes to
interaction with matter.

00:52:19.210 --> 00:52:21.710
Because visible
light, the photon,

00:52:21.710 --> 00:52:25.190
each photon that impinges
